Great American Bank say di board don approve di formation of one holding company wey be sey e go give di bank money to take dey do no be traditional banking activity under new federal law.

Di proposed holding company primary purpose na to allow Great American to continue to dey do real estate development work o.

Dose activity generate $26.1 million in operating profit last year.

But according by Big American, dat one no dey count towards San Diego savings bank account, under 1989 Federal Law.

Di new real estate unit go get separate capital structure to comply with di law.

Di proposed holding company go also consolidate Great American Bank for San Diego, and im Tucson, Ariz, savings bank for one single, federal chartered institution for San Diego.

Confirmation suppose save $1 million a year for admin costs, one Great American spokesperson yarn.

